    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained. The exterior paint still holds a high gloss, though close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the front end and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and is ready for its next owner with no immediate service needs.",
